      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2021 Lexus RX 350 F-Sport is the definition of a 'time capsule' vehicle. Finished in Ultra White over a flawless Circuit Red leather interior, it has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the leather bolsters show zero signs of wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it still carries that signature new-car scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach. It features a complete, documented service history exclusively through Lexus dealerships, with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time. The engine bay is spotless, the tires have nearly full tread, and the drive is as smooth and quiet as the day it left the factory. Included are all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
