    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original factory luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. This is an uncompromising opportunity for those who demand excellence in both performance and presentation.",
