    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade A80 chassis in an unmodified state. Powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, the sequential twin-turbocharging system delivers linear boost across the rev range, mated to the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual. This example retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and four-piston front calipers. Every body panel features matching VIN tags, confirming a history free of structural compromise. The suspension remains tight, utilizing the original double-wishbone configuration for precise lateral stability. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning collector.",
